genresAdvancedInfo.name: gambian pop
genresAdvancedInfo.description: Gambian pop is a genre that blends traditional Gambian rhythms and melodies with contemporary pop music. It is characterized by upbeat, catchy melodies and lyrics that often celebrate love, relationships, and partying. Gambian pop artists often incorporate traditional instruments, such as the kora and balafon, into their music to create a unique sound that reflects their cultural heritage.
